    },
    {
      "slide_index": 4,
      "slide_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_0_10",
      "elements": [
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_0_11",
          "type": "IMAGE",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_0_12",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Inform"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_0_13",
          "type": "ROUND_RECTANGLE",
          "text": "Play Audio"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_0_14",
          "type": "IMAGE",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_0_17",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Turn scattered data into clear, reliable answers that support faster learning, smarter decisions, and confident conversations."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_3_21",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "5"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slide_index": 5,
      "slide_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_7",
      "elements": [
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_8",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Advisors prepare for client meetings by pulling data from CRM, portfolio tools, and emails. This takes time and risks missing key details, especially for complex retirement plans."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_9",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Before a review, advisors upload CRM exports, portfolio summaries, and recent communications into the AI assistant. It generates a concise client snapshot that includes retirement goals, key financial metrics, recent changes, and flagged risks. The output is formatted as a meeting brief that can be shared across advisors and support staff."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_10",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Client Snapshot in Seconds"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_3_11",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "6"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slide_index": 6,
      "slide_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_0",
      "elements": [
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_1",
          "type": "IMAGE",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_2",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Create & Edit"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_3",
          "type": "ROUND_RECTANGLE",
          "text": "Play Audio"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_4",
          "type": "IMAGE",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_7",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Generate polished content from rough ideas, then refine and enhance it to match your goals."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_3_22",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "7"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slide_index": 7,
      "slide_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_13",
      "elements": [
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_14",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "After client meetings, advisors must manually draft follow-up emails and plan summaries. This leads to inconsistent quality, delayed communication, and duplicated effort across the team. Important recommendations may also be communicated differently depending on the advisor."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_15",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Following a meeting, notes, planning outputs, and key decisions are fed into the AI. It produces a polished client summary, including action items, strategy explanations, and next steps. The tone can be adjusted for clarity and personalization, and outputs are ready for email or PDF delivery."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_16",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Automated Plan Summaries"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_3_12",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "8"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slide_index": 8,
      "slide_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_8",
      "elements": [
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_9",
          "type": "IMAGE",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_10",
          "type": "ROUND_RECTANGLE",
          "text": "Play Audio"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_11",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Organize"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_12",
          "type": "IMAGE",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_15",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Bring order to complexity by grouping, prioritizing, and structuring information for better visibility and decision-making."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_3_23",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "9"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slide_index": 9,
      "slide_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_19",
      "elements": [
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_20",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Meeting notes are often unstructured and stored in different formats, making it difficult to track next steps. Advisors and operations teams may miss follow-ups or duplicate work, leading to inefficiencies and a fragmented client experience."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_21",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Raw meeting notes and call transcripts are input into the AI assistant. It organizes the information into categorized action items, assigns responsibilities, and prioritizes tasks. Outputs can be integrated into task management tools or CRM systems."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_22",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Actionable Meeting Outputs"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_3_13",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "10"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slide_index": 10,
      "slide_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_16",
      "elements": [
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_17",
          "type": "IMAGE",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_18",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Transform"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_19",
          "type": "ROUND_RECTANGLE",
          "text": "Play Audio"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_20",
          "type": "IMAGE",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_23",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Convert content across formats, tones, or audiences to ensure your message fits any context or communication need."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_3_24",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "11"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slide_index": 11,
      "slide_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_25",
      "elements": [
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_26",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Advisors frequently need to explain complex retirement strategies in simple terms. Translating technical content into client-friendly language takes time and can vary in clarity."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_27",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Detailed financial plans, spreadsheets, or technical notes are provided to the AI. It converts them into simplified explanations, visual summaries, or presentation-ready content tailored to the client\u2019s level of understanding."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_28",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Simplified Client Explanations"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_3_14",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "12"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slide_index": 12,
      "slide_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_24",
      "elements": [
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_25",
          "type": "IMAGE",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_26",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Analyze"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_27",
          "type": "ROUND_RECTANGLE",
          "text": "Play Audio"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_28",
          "type": "IMAGE",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_31",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Turn raw information into clear perspectives by assessing trade-offs, risks, and opportunities with structured reasoning."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_3_25",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "13"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slide_index": 13,
      "slide_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_31",
      "elements": [
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_32",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Advisors often evaluate multiple retirement strategies. Comparing these scenarios manually can be time-intensive and may limit the depth of analysis during client discussions."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_33",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Financial data, assumptions, and multiple planning scenarios are entered into the AI assistant. It analyzes the options, highlights trade-offs, and summarizes key differences in outcomes such as income stability, tax impact, and risk exposure."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_34",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Strategy Comparison Insights"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_3_15",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "14"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slide_index": 14,
      "slide_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_32",
      "elements": [
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_33",
          "type": "IMAGE",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_34",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Personify or Simulate"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_35",
          "type": "ROUND_RECTANGLE",
          "text": "Play Audio"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_36",
          "type": "IMAGE",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_39",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Practice communication, explore viewpoints, and model behaviors through realistic, role-based AI-driven simulations."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_3_26",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "15"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slide_index": 15,
      "slide_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_37",
      "elements": [
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_38",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Advisors face challenges when explaining complex strategies or handling sensitive client concerns. Training opportunities may be limited."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_39",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "The AI is prompted with client personas and simulates realistic conversations. Advisors practice explaining strategies, responding to objections, and refining their communication style."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_40",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Client Conversation Practice"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_3_16",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "16"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slide_index": 16,
      "slide_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_40",
      "elements": [
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_41",
          "type": "IMAGE",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_42",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Explore & Guide"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_43",
          "type": "ROUND_RECTANGLE",
          "text": "Play Audio"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_44",
          "type": "IMAGE",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_2_47",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Move from uncertainty to direction by exploring possibilities and building structured plans with guided support."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_3_27",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "17"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slide_index": 17,
      "slide_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_43",
      "elements": [
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_44",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "As the firm scales, leadership must refine workflows across onboarding, planning, and operations. Identifying inefficiencies can be complex."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_45",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Leaders provide descriptions of current workflows and pain points. The AI generates structured improvement plans, suggesting process changes, automation opportunities, and implementation roadmaps."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g36bad6684b2_0_46",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Workflow Optimization Roadmaps"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g3d16c9cd8cb_3_17",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "18"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "slide_index": 18,
      "slide_id": "g369bbc18a25_2_87",
      "elements": [
        {
          "object_id": "g369bbc18a25_2_88",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Start your personalized path to \u000bAI productivity and next-level results."
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g369bbc18a25_2_90",
          "type": "TEXT_BOX",
          "text": "Next Moves"
        },
        {
          "object_id": "g36c4f10f800_2_36",
          "type": "ROUND_RECTANGLE",
          "text": "Play Audio"
        },
        {
